{"tid":1692231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拜仁炒尼高高華　傳摩連奴有機接任","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T14:38:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"494870d6b727c95f32d653d03bddbeffeae01448","tid":1692231,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"拜仁正式宣布，辭退領隊尼高高華。拜仁於周六以1：5大敗予法蘭克福，高層和高華開會後，決定和這位克羅地亞籍主帥分道揚鑣。<br />\n<br />\n今年48歲的高華，於18年接任拜仁主帥，上季帶領拜仁力壓多蒙特贏得德甲冠軍，另外亦獲取德國盃錦標。雖然成為雙冠王，但拜仁霸氣已不及以往。本季踢了10場聯賽，拜om已事2場，剛過去敗仗更令球隊高層不可接受。<br />\n<br />\n高華表示：「這次決定對拜仁來說，是個正確的決定。球會近期的差劣戰績和表現，令我要承受這個惡果。我和羅拔高華，多謝拜仁高層這1年半以來的照顧。」尼高高華離開後，摩連奴、艾歷尼及普捷天奴成為接任大熱。(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=c50a330e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"5795d78059f4de9ab92bbd707d9e37d65daf8d9d","tid":1692231,"uid":235174,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:48:58.000Z","msg":"大材小用, 教阿仙奴或者熱刺有挑戰性好多"},{"pid":"e9305c66a94258c498c66923bf74859aea10c2bf","tid":1692231,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"不敢想像摩佬玩德甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff4bdade5896dcd101bf631ebd71e835cca9627","tid":1692231,"uid":56459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"摩佬想贏哂四大聯賽冠軍"},{"pid":"b95dc61ba3e59266e572c51a2e1c09af832fd623","tid":1692231,"uid":60061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"學左德文未，未學就1年已經開始提25仔"},{"pid":"8b49f9f49ed583bb429d85742497ff2b2328ee3b","tid":1692231,"uid":60061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95dc61ba3e59266e572c51